<ab type="dharani">唵僧賀囉渴誐<lb
 n="0719a29" ed="T"/></ab>
<ab type="prose">為令智劍堅固不散復誦真言曰。<pb n="0719b" id="T20.1175.0719b" ed="T"/><lb
